Privacy Policy

Last updated: 14 April 2024

Welcome to Coloured To Do List App! This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, share, and protect information about you through our mobile application. By using Coloured To Do List, you agree to the terms of this Privacy Policy.

1. Information We Collect

We may collect the following types of information when you use Coloured To Do List:

Personal Information: This may include your name, email address, and payment information when you make purchases within the app.
Device Information: We may collect information about your device, such as its unique identifier, operating system version, and IP address.
Usage Data: We gather data on how you interact with our app, including which features you use and how often.
2. How We Collect Information

We collect information directly from you when you use our app, as well as automatically through cookies and similar technologies.

3. How We Use Information

We use the information we collect to:

Provide and maintain the app's functionality.
Customize your experience within the app.
Analyze usage patterns and improve our services.
Communicate with you about updates, promotions, and other relevant information.
4. Third-Party Access

No Third-party Access in Coloured To Do List

5. Data Sharing

We do not sell or rent your personal information to third parties. However, we may share data with trusted partners for business purposes, such as processing payments or providing customer support.

6. User Controls

You have the right to access, update, or delete your personal information. You can also opt-out of certain data collection activities by adjusting your device settings or contacting us directly.

7. Data Security

We take reasonable measures to protect your information from unauthorized access, disclosure, or alteration. However, no method of transmission over the internet is 100% secure, and we cannot guarantee absolute security.

8. Policy Updates

We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes will be posted on this page, and you will be notified of significant updates.

9. Contact Us

If you have any questions or concerns about our Privacy Policy, please contact us at info@codebright.sg.

10. Legal Compliance

Coloured To Do List complies with applicable privacy laws, including the General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR) and the California Consumer Privacy Act (CCPA).
